Content:
@everyone - The Crowd Supply campaign for GF180MCU Run #2 is now open at https://buy.wafer.space and people can currently purchase slots at the early bird pricing (with half slots at **only** $4k USD for 1,000 parts)!

The website at https://wafer.space has also been updated with this new information and count down timers.

A general email is likely to go out to everyone who has requested to be emailed tomorrow. So far indications have been that half slots are going to be very popular, so get your half slots before they sell out!
